        "reasoning_content": "I should also clear any corrupted program cache entries from the previous bad program hash, and check if the old program override might still be an issue. The install should have set a new program ove...I see the issue now— the middle pan isn't translating anymore, and the program is auto-exiting after a while. The root cause is likely a leftover corrupted program cache from the old hash, combined with the async upload/writeback during the previous install.\n\nSince the install should have updated the program override to the new hash and purged the old corrupted cache entry, the next step is to make sure the local cache is fully clean. The old program hash entry might still be hanging around in the cache, causing the program to load the corrupted version and crash.\n\nAlso, the user should restart the VM."
